<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">喂<tag a="110" b="0" />我問你，<delay8 />
你有沒有遇過，
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可怕到讓你臉色發青的事啊？</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">可怕的事？<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />應該是我晚上散步散到一半，<delay8 />
結果在一片漆黑中碰到
跳舞跳得入迷的<tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" />那時吧！<anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><gender3 m="他" f="她" />說只要在外面練習<delay8 />就可以全神貫注，<delay20 />
我想那大概是<delay8 />
那傢伙獨特的集中精神方法吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />原來是這樣啊，<delay20 />
聽起來的確很嚇人啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">可怕的事？<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" />前陣子<delay8 />
在讀一本叫做
「搏命<tag a="135" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />」的書<anim id="Shocked" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很擔心，<delay8 />
那傢伙是不是想要做什麼<delay8 />
荒唐事啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">可怕的事？<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前陣子<delay8 />我沒鎖門
就外出了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 /><anim id="OhGeez" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果什麼東西都沒被偷走耶──！<pageBreak />不過，<delay8 />
<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />有被吃過的痕跡。<delay20 /><anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是我不記得我有吃啊。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
要用什麼來比輸贏啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 03 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay8 />我想想喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_3 arg="8" />啊，<delay8 /><20_3 arg="6" /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<20_2 arg="4" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你來得正好！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我正好<delay8 />和<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />在討論，<delay8 />
哪種比賽最適合<delay20 />
用來決定誰是最強的男子漢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，如果是你，
你覺得比什麼最好？</message>
	<message label="102_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">腕力比賽</message>
	<message label="102_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">接龍比賽</message>
	<message label="102_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">唱歌比賽</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />腕力比賽啊──！<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="5" />這可是我拿手的喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />靠著平時健身
鍛鍊出的<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這身肌肉！<delay40 />
是不會簡單敗北的喔──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">哦？<delay8 /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可別太小看我哦？<delay20 /><20_2 arg="7" />
我<delay8 />對比腕力
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是很有自信的啊！</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接龍比賽啊──！<delay20 />
<20_2 arg="5" />普通的接龍太無趣了，<delay8 />
<anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我們來比「肌肉接龍」<delay8 />怎麼樣──！？<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />規則是
只能用肌肉的名稱接龍！<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺很有威力吧──！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你這笨蛋！<delay40 />
<20_2 arg="7" />那種接龍<delay8 />根本就沒辦法分出勝負！<pageBreak />腹肌<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
肱二頭肌<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />馬上就接不下去了啊！</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唱歌比賽啊──！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唱歌的基本技巧就是腹式呼吸法啊！<delay20 />
<20_2 arg="5" />讓聲音從腹部的深處像這樣<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><10_10 /><size value="150" />肱二頭肌～♪<anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><size value="100" /></message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還以為我的耳膜要破啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />又不是聲音大就會贏！</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你聽好啦，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" />！<delay20 />
厲害的男人啊，<delay8 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是有力氣還不夠。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />首先<delay8 />要靠自己的氣魄
壓制對方。<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣<delay8 />才能算是真正的男子漢，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只用氣魄<delay8 />壓制對方～？<10_4 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那要怎麼鍛鍊啊？<delay8 />
我<delay8 />有聽沒有懂啊！？</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別想得太複雜，<delay8 />很簡單的啦。<delay20 />
就算對方瞪著你也不要慌張，<delay8 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要表現出坦蕩蕩的樣子！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再來就是語氣。<delay20 />
跟對方說話時<delay8 />
要用<delay8 />清晰宏亮的聲音！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來是這樣啊──！<delay20 />
我的確從<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />身上<delay8 />
感受到威力囉！<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我能不能模仿<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />你的口頭禪啊～？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得要是我用<delay8 />
「<tag a="110" b="5" />」，
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />會更有<delay8 />氣魄啊──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好啊！<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別客氣儘管用吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
